name: Pipeline Construction Set
body:
### Welcome to the Technical Artist's best friend.
This is how you get it:

```
$ cd your_repo_root/repo_name
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```

If you're using the GitHub for Mac, simply sync your repository and you'll see the new branch.



### Authors and Contributors
Author @CountZer0
Contributors @cakesson, @SethGibson



### Support or Contact
Email jason@jason-parks.com
tagline: Code base for Art Pipelines creating an easy to use API for Technical Artists.
